articles.value: Ten Underplayed Cards for SpongeBob Squarepants (AKA Jodah, the Unifier)
articles.excerpt: Let's take a look at ten cards that are underplayed with the new Secret Lair commander SpongeBob Squarepants, a reskin of Jodah, the Unifier.
Grab your shovel and unearth some good stuff to send your opponents to the graveyard!

articles.value: Alesha, Who Laughs at Fate Commander Deck Tech
articles.excerpt: Alesha, Who Laughs at Fate doesn't just laugh at fate, she triggers on attack. Figure out how to make the most of her unique effects with this Commander deck!

articles.value: Conditions Allow - Alesha, Who Laughs at Fate EDH
articles.excerpt: Ben builds the new Rakdos version of Aelsha from Foundations in the latest edition of Conditions Allow.
Build decks where you can cast from exile, build up +1/+1 counters and more with these three Foundations commanders!
